FOR HONOR's Open Beta is finally here, and I couldn't wait to get my hands on it. After all the research I did on these historic warriors I needed to find out if it gives me a leg up on the competition. I will of course be playing as a Samurai. Join us for what promises to be a fiercely fun episode!
